short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows user to search for and navigate to a specific tab out of many

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows the user to search all open tabs’ titles and URLs for a string. Not only does it search all tabs in the open window it will search all tabs in all windows. Help using the application can be found in by clicking the “?” button in the upper right-hand corner. The extension can also be accessed by pressing Ctrl+Shift+F.
